{"comments":"TimeAuthority — Distributed time coordination for billion-agent scale.\n\n## Purpose\n\nAt billion-agent scale, time synchronization becomes critical:\n\n- Agents across the globe must agree on \"when\" events occur\n- Animation frames must be deterministic across viewports\n- Causal ordering must be preserved for collaborative editing\n- Network latency must be compensated for smooth coordination\n\n## Architecture\n\nThis leader module re-exports functionality from submodules:\n\n- **Lamport**: Scalar logical clocks and logical time with agent ID\n- **VectorClock**: Vector clocks for detecting concurrent events\n- **ClockSync**: NTP-style wall-clock synchronization\n- **FrameSchedule**: Deterministic frame timing for animation\n\n## Usage\n\nImport this module to get all time-related types and functions.\nFor finer-grained imports, use the submodules directly.\n","declarations":[{"children":[{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["agentId",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Distributed","TimeAuthority","Lamport"],"AgentId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["currentTime",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Distributed","TimeAuthority","ClockSync"],"FrameTime"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"declType":"dataConstructor"},"sourceSpan":{"end":[148,19],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Distributed/TimeAuthority.purs","start":[148,3]},"title":"LocalAuthority"},{"comments":null,"info":{"arguments":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["serverId",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Distributed","TimeAuthority","Lamport"],"AgentId"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["serverTime",{"annotation":[],"conten